data.description: Beautiful single-family home with three bedrooms and two bathrooms, everting is all remodeled kitchen all bathrooms with title and glass, very ample back yard. Deerwood community offers a swimming pool tennis court etc.. This property is located just minutes away from Florida Turnpike and Metro Zoo and walking distance to shopping center and resturants.
